<h2>What Does SEO Service in Kenya Cost?</h2>
<p>Honest pricing for SEO in Kenya:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Basic local SEO</strong> (Google Business Profile optimisation, on-page fixes): Ksh 8,000–15,000 one-time</li>
  <li><strong>Monthly SEO management</strong> (ongoing content, links, reporting): Ksh 8,000–25,000/month</li>
  <li><strong>Full SEO campaign</strong> (technical + content + links + local): Ksh 20,000–50,000/month</li>
</ul>
<p>Be wary of agencies offering "SEO packages" for Ksh 2,000–5,000/month. At that price, no meaningful work is being done.</p>

<h2>Red Flags When Hiring an SEO Provider in Kenya</h2>
<ul>
  <li>"We guarantee page 1 in 30 days" — no one can guarantee Google rankings</li>
  <li>No monthly reporting — you should see keyword rankings, traffic, and what work was done</li>
  <li>Link farms and spammy backlinks — these lead to Google penalties</li>
  <li>Automated, AI-generated content published at scale — Google penalises thin, low-quality content</li>
  <li>No mention of technical SEO — fixing your site's technical foundation is step one</li>
</ul>

